# Amazon

Admin username : mysite   password : 0000

admin operations ---> 1.List all merchants    
                      2.merchants waiting list(approve/disapprove)      
                      3.delete merchant   
                      4.View all products(lists all merchants products)
                      
merchant login ---> 1.Existing merchant(login with credentials)
                    2.new merchant(signup and wait for admin approval)

merchant operations ----> 1.Add product  
                         2.review product(list all of his products)  
                         3.update product(update desired products)
        
user login ---> 1.Existing user(login with credentials)
                2.new user(signup)

user operations ---> 1.available products(lists all products && adding products to cart)     
                     2.go to cart(buying from cart either using wallet/COD)   
                     3.check wallet balance(check/add money)      
                     4.order history(previous orders)
